cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.PL

This paper deals with the formalism for describing the evolution of biological systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also introduces a type discipline to guarantee the soundness of reduction rules, which is related to the field of logic in computer science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper uses term rewriting rules, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and formal language theory (cs.DS). Finally, the paper models a toy system, which involves programming language concepts (cs.PL).
